Description: Snapmaker Orca - 3D Printing Slicer
 Snapmaker Orca is a 3D printer slicer based on OrcaSlicer/BambuStudio.
 It converts 3D models into G-code instructions for 3D printing,
 supporting STL, 3MF, OBJ, AMF, and STEP file formats.
